item.title: How do I made my client load the cache from more than one place like mopar?
item.dc:creator: @llib llib
item.description:
@llib wrote:

Mopar loads its cache from .mpr_file_store_32 no other place. If that file isn’t found, then it downloads the cache and puts it there. It doesn’t load it from multiple places.
